 <title>About This Guide</title>
 <para>
  &prod-descr-short;
 </para>
 <para>
  This guide helps cloud users to launch instances, manage volumes and track
  usage. Most of these tasks can either be achieved with the Web interface
  (the &productname; &dash;) or the &ostack; command line tools.
 </para>
 <para>
  <remark>taroth 2012-06-26: FIXME - describe parts, if available in 
 manual</remark>
  This guide is divided into the following parts:
 </para>
